rg/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French swimmer picked up \\u20ac80,000 (\\u00a368,500) for each of his four gold medals, plus an additional \\u20ac20,000 (\\u00a317,000).\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2903, \"end\": 2909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8529575701187502, \"rank\": 0.16496247434085134, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In sixth place, Georgia's trio of gold medal winners -Lasha Bekauri, Geno Petriashvili and Lasha Talakhadze - have each been given one million Georgian lari, which is approximately \\u00a3289,000.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3035, \"end\": 3042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9216485387940717, \"rank\": 0.05094677556118274, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3073, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Bekauri\", \"score\": 0.9999999461615531, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lasha Bekauri\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Bekauri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Bekauri\"}, {\"begin\": 3088, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geno_Petriashvili\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Geno Petriashvili\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geno_Petriashvili\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geno_Petriashvili\"}, {\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Talakhadze\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lasha Talakhadze\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2156